# UP CAF AI Dashboard — Design System

## Identità visiva

Dashboard operativa per UP CAF (CAF + Patronato), uso interno, operatore singolo su desktop.
Stile: sidebar scura con logo, area principale su canvas caldo, bordi invece di shadow, pill buttons.
Ispirazione: Dub (border-first), Apple España (pill 980px), Cursor.sh (parchment canvas), Dovetail (JetBrains Mono labels).

---

## Palette colori

### Sidebar (sempre scura)
```
--sb-bg:            #1a1917   /* background sidebar */
--sb-border:        rgba(255,255,255,0.06)
--sb-item-active:   rgba(255,255,255,0.08)
--sb-text-active:   #f7f7f4
--sb-text-muted:    rgba(255,255,255,0.45)
--sb-label-muted:   rgba(255,255,255,0.25)
--sb-live:          #00A63D
```

### Dashboard (canvas caldo)
```
--canvas:           #f7f7f4   /* background pagina */
--surface:          #ffffff   /* card, topbar */
--surface-alt:      #f2f1ed   /* righe alternate, input bg */
--border:           #e5e5e5   /* bordi card e righe */
--border-soft:      #cdcdc9   /* bordi input, ghost button */
--text-primary:     #26251e   /* testo principale */
--text-muted:       #7a7974   /* testo secondario, label */
```

### Accenti funzionali (usare con parsimonia)
```
--accent-blue:      #2E6FF2   /* btn primario, badge sidebar normative */
--accent-amber:     #c08532   /* badge sidebar handoff, stat warning */
--accent-green:     #34785c   /* stat positivi, badge successo */
--accent-red:       #b52040   /* badge urgente */
```

### Badge pill (tinte morbide)
```
/* In attesa */   background: rgba(192,133,50,0.1);  color: #a06820;
/* Urgente */     background: rgba(207,45,86,0.1);   color: #b52040;
/* Successo */    background: rgba(52,120,92,0.1);   color: #2a6b50;
