```

---

## Tipografia

```
--font-sans:  'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif
--font-mono:  'JetBrains Mono', monospace
```

### Scale
| Ruolo | Font | Size | Weight | Note |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Stat number | Inter | 24px | 400 | tracking -0.6px |
| Card title | Inter | 11px | 500 | tracking -0.15px |
| Body / nome | Inter | 11px | 400–500 | tracking -0.15px |
| Button | Inter | 11px | 400 | tracking -0.15px |
| Page title (topbar) | Inter | 13px | 500 | tracking -0.2px |
| Eyebrow / label | JetBrains Mono | 9px | 400 | uppercase, spacing 0.7px |
| Meta / sub | JetBrains Mono | 9px | 400 | spacing 0.3–0.5px |
| Nav sidebar | Inter | 12px | 400 | tracking -0.1px |
| Nav label sidebar | JetBrains Mono | 8px | 400 | uppercase, spacing 0.7px |

**Regola:** JetBrains Mono SOLO per etichette categoria, metadati, date, label tecnici.
Inter per tutto il resto.

