## Layout

### Struttura shell
```
.shell {
  display: flex;
  /* sidebar fissa a sinistra, main area flex: 1 */
}
```

### Sidebar
```
width: 160px;
min-width: 160px;
background: #1a1917;
display: flex;
flex-direction: column;
```

- **Brand area**: logo `logo-white.png` con `mix-blend-mode: screen` (elimina sfondo nero PNG)
- **Nav items**: gap 8px, padding 7px 10px, border-radius 8px
- **Active state**: `background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`, text bianco pieno
- **Live indicator**: in fondo, dot verde `#00A63D`, testo mono muted
- **Badge count**: pill 9999px, blu o amber, margin-left: auto

### Topbar
```
background: #fff;
border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
padding: 10px 16px;
```

### Stats grid
```
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
gap: 8px;
padding: 12px 16px;
background: #f7f7f4;
```

### Card body
```
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
gap: 8px;
padding: 0 16px 16px;
```

### Card
```
background: #fff;
border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
border-radius: 12px;
padding: 12px;
box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 0 1px 3px;
```

### Riga item (dentro card)
```
background: #f7f7f4;
border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
border-radius: 8px;
padding: 7px 9px;
margin-bottom: 4px;
```

