## Componenti

### Stat card
```css
.stat {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 10px 12px;
  box-shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.03) 0 1px 2px;
}
.stat-value {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: #26251e;
  letter-spacing: -0.6px;
  line-height: 1.1;
}
.stat-label {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  color: #7a7974;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.6px;
}
```

### Pill badge (stato)
```css
.pill {
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 9999px;
}
```

### Buttons — REGOLA CRITICA: border-radius 980px (Apple España)
```css
/* Primario blu */
.btn-primary {
  background: #2E6FF2;
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 400;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  border-radius: 980px;
  border: none;
}

/* Secondario ink */
.btn-ink {
  background: #26251e;
  color: #f7f7f4;
  font-size: 11px;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  border-radius: 980px;
  border: none;
}

/* Ghost */
.btn-ghost {
  background: #f2f1ed;
  color: #26251e;
  font-size: 11px;
  padding: 6px 14px;
  border-radius: 980px;
  border: 1px solid #cdcdc9;
}
```

### Input / Query
```css
.input {
  background: #f7f7f4;
  border: 1px solid #cdcdc9;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 8px 12px;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: #7a7974;
  font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
}
```

### Card eyebrow (titolo sezione dentro card)
```css
.card-eyebrow {
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 9px;
  color: #7a7974;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.7px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
```

